OL,3,CMan guilty of manslaughter after
OL,4,Cstabbing in St Pauls
OL,6,FA man has been found guilty of
OL,7,Fmanslaughter following the death of
OL,8,FAlex Mamwa in St Pauls on 5 March 2024.
OL,10,FDavid Malcolm, 43, appeared at Bristol
OL,11,FCrown Court on Friday 13 September.
OL,13,FHe claimed he acted in self-defence
OL,14,Fwhen he fatally stabbed Alex, but said
OL,15,Fhe had not intended to kill or
OL,16,Fseriously harm the 30-year-old.
OL,18,FMalcolm was acquitted of murder but
OL,19,Ffound guilty of manslaughter and
OL,20,Fpossession of a bladed article.
