OL,3,CMan guilty of manslaughter after
OL,4,Cstabbing in St Pauls
OL,6,FThe jury heard the pair had a long-
OL,7,Frunning personal dispute which, on
OL,8,FValentine's Day this year, resulted in
OL,9,Fan altercation in Grosvenor Road, St
OL,10,FPauls in which Malcolm sustained a cut
OL,11,Fabove his eye.
OL,13,FThe day after, Malcolm asked his
OL,14,Fgirlfriend to buy him a baseball bat
OL,15,Fwhich he later combined with car parts
OL,16,Fto create a "fearsome" weapon.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
