OL,3,CMan guilty of manslaughter after
OL,4,Cstabbing in St Pauls
OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Phil Walker,
OL,7,Fthe senior investigating officer,
OL,8,Fsaid: "David Malcolm's actions that
OL,9,Fnight tragically led to the death of a
OL,10,Fyoung man and the loss of a much-loved
OL,11,Ffriend and family member to those who
OL,12,Fknew him.
OL,14,F"I'd like to pay tribute to Alex's
OL,15,Ffamily who have gone through a
OL,16,Fhorrendous ordeal over the past six
OL,17,Fmonths and who continue to process the
OL,18,Fevents of that night. They have acted
OL,19,Fwith incredible dignity throughout
OL,20,Fand, including whilst listening to the
OL,21,Fevidence in court.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
