OL,3,CMan guilty of manslaughter after
OL,4,Cstabbing in St Pauls
OL,6,F"And I'd also like to thank the
OL,7,Fcommunity of St Pauls for their
OL,8,Fsupport and everyone who tried to help
OL,9,FAlex or who came forward with
OL,10,Finformation for our investigation.
OL,11,FThis support was invaluable in
OL,12,Fsecuring this outcome and shows how
OL,13,Fvital it is in helping us bring
OL,14,Fjustice for families.
OL,16,F"Finally, I once again extend my
OL,17,Fsincere condolences to Alex's friends
OL,18,Fand family at what continues to be a
OL,19,Fdifficult time for them all."
